{
  "title": "Magnificently Crunchy Chinese Malai Hot Pot",
  "description": "A garlicky and crunchy Chinese hot pot dish featuring malai and char-grill-yang flavors, perfect for a cozy dinner",
  "cuisine": "Chinese",
